location.fullValue: Everson Plan, Badger Mountain South - West Village

data.description: MLS# 273637  NEW PRICE - 2.21.24!!  Your search is over!  This one owner home has everything you are looking for.  Located on a corner lot across the street from Celebration Park in Badger Mountain South's "West Vineyard" subdivision, this one level home is immaculate inside & out.   This home has 3 bedrooms and 1.75 baths inside with an extra half bath in the garage.  The thoughtfully designed split bedroom floor plan affords functionality and privacy for all.  The spacious great room has a gas fireplace for cozy cool evenings. The large well appointed kitchen has granite counters, custom cabinetry with full height backsplash, Bosch stainless steel appliances, pantry and a large storage center island and pendant lighting.  Enjoy entertaining in the spacious dining area adjacent to the kitchen and great room.  The primary bedroom has a wonderful bath with dual sinks, granite counters, large shower with double benches and a spacious walk in closet with built ins.  The utility room has a utility sink, large folding counter and built in washer & dryer risers for easy access to front loading washer & dryer.  The hobbyist will love the 3rd garage bay; perfect for wood working or other hobbies - plus a half bath too.  Additional home amenities include: hand scraped laminate flooring, geo thermal heating and cooling, RING doorbell and Green Built & Energy Star features.  And for that added feeling of security, this home has an interior sprinkler system too.  Enjoy sunsets on the front porch or endless shady evenings on the large 18x14 covered back patio.  The property has timed underground sprinklers and a fenced back yard too!  With easy freeway access, miles of walking paths and a short walk to the Country Mercantile for ice cream, candies, pastries, breads, fresh produce gifts and more!  You may never want (or have) to leave!
